_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/646762079\"><i>Social lives in language--sociolinguistics and multilingual speech communities&#160;: celebrating the work of Gillian Sankoff</i></a>. Sankoff, Gillian., Meyerhoff, Miriam., Nagy, Naomi. Amsterdam: John Benjamins. 2008. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/9789027218636\" title=\"Special:BookSources/9789027218636\">9789027218636</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/OCLC\" title=\"OCLC\">OCLC</a>&#160;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//www.worldcat.org/oclc/646762079\">646762079</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Social+lives+in+language--sociolinguistics+and+multilingual+speech+communities+%3A+celebrating+the+work+of+Gillian+Sankoff&amp;rft.place=Amsterdam&amp;rft.pub=John+Benjamins&amp;rft.date=2008&amp;rft_id=info%3Aoclcnum%2F646762079&amp;rft.isbn=9789027218636&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldcat.org%2Foclc%2F646762079&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AGillian+Sankoff\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://frit.indiana.edu/docs/newsletters/2013-summer-frit.pdf\">\"NWAV 41 at Indiana University\"</a> <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(PDF)</span>. <i>2013 summer FRIT newsletter IU</i>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=2013+summer+FRIT+newsletter+IU&amp;rft.atitle=NWAV+41+at+Indiana+University&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2F